message.entry: The StringSetGF lists of grandfathered and new values must be non-empty equal length cell arrays of character vectors or string vectors.
StringSetGF requires three sets of entries, each specified by a cell array of character vectors or a string array.
The new values list in the StringSetGF contains invalid entries.
The old values list in the StringSetGF contains invalid entries.
The old an new values list cannot contain empty entries.
StringSetGF grandfathered values must be case-insensitive unique.
The set of warnings must have the same length as the number of grandfathered values and must be specified as a cell array of character vectors or a string array.
